room_title: Escape room "The Cleaners" by Enter Locked Escape Rooms in Jackson (MS)
room_description: You are a G-man working undercover in a vast criminal network, trying to take down notorious mafia kingpin Jimmy "The Xyster" Nicoletti. A lead in the case to Nicoletti's laundering scheme is about to blow this case wide open. But be careful, Jimmy has been tipped off and is heading your way. You have 1 hour to get to his stash and get out of there or you'll be hung out to dry.
